text: tavrataya pahala vimata pera israyilvarunta sæma aharayakma anumata kara tibuni. ehet (yakub vana) israyilvarun tamanta tahanam kara gat dæya hæra. (ebævin meyata venas andamin pavasana yudevvanta nabiye!) oba mese kiyanu: “oba ættenma satyaya prakasa karannan vasayen sitinnehu nam, tavrataya genævit eya kiyava penvanu”
